               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla Takla Hāymānot “Vita of Takla Haymanot” (fols. 3ra-75va)&#xD;
                     II) Maṣḥafa lǝdätu la-ʾabuna Takla Hāymānot “Book of the Genealogy of Takla
                     Haymanot” (fols. 75va-76vb)&#xD; - Genealogy of Takla Hāymānot (fols.
                     75va-76vb)&#xD; &#xD; Additiones 1-2; colophon.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="3ra" to="76vb"/>
